<indentation-standards>

<rules>
- Always use 2 spaces for indentation in JavaScript and TypeScript files
- Never use tabs for indentation
- Configure your editor to insert spaces when pressing the tab key
- Each nested level increases indentation by exactly 2 spaces
- Maintain consistent indentation throughout the entire file
</rules>

